extension_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Extensions provide a passive income for a variety of resources.
extension_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Dobudówki dają pasywny przyrost różnego rodzaju surowców.

conversion_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Convert this house to an artisan workshop. Peasants become skilled artisans, and are forever removed from the common workforce. {br} Because there is no going back, a minimum of 1 extra peasant is required in the Region to enable construction.

upgrade_2_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Required to increase the <h>SETTLEMENT LEVEL</>. Provides better fighting equipment if levied. {br}{br}All of the <h>REQUIREMENTS</> must be met.

upgrade_6_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Grants a DEVELOPMENT POINT, provides living space for one more Family, and enables Artisan Conversions [Bakery/Brewery/Tailor/Blacksmith].

upgrade_8_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Increases PANTRY LIMIT to 1500 and provides 1 extra HANDCART.

upgrade_10_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Trading carts allow to transport up to 20 goods in one trip. {br}{br}<r>WORK IN PROGRESS -LOCKED</>.

upgrade_11_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Adds a LIVESTOCK WORKER slot and enables ploughing large fields significantly faster.

upgrade_12_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Grants living space for another family.

upgrade_13_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Invites an off map trader to import a single OX to this town. Available once every 30 days.

upgrade_14_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Increases the STABLE SPACE of the building by 2.

upgrade_101_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Provides Eggs, consistently throughout the whole year.

upgrade_108_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Produces VEGETABLES. {br}Doesn't provide yields in the WINTER.

not_enough_workers.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: All workers busy / waiting its turn
not_enough_workers.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Brak rąk do pracy / czeka na swoją kolej

overlaps_habitat.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Overlaps wild animal habitat. May cause migration!
overlaps_habitat.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Budynek nachodzi na tereny lęgowe zwierzyny łownej. To może spowodować migrację!

autoSupply_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: A worker will travel to the nearest TRADEPOINT in order to buy whatever COMMODITES the peasants require. The region will pay in SILVER.
autoSupply_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Pracownik będzie podróżował do najbliższego Tradepoint w celu zakupu TOWARÓW , których potrzebują mieszkańcy. Region zapłaci za to SREBREM.

tip_newPlayers_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Peasants need FOOD and WOOD to survive. {br}{br} Farming takes time, so a good place to start is a LOGGING CAMP and a HUNTING CAMP. {br}{br} After you got the basic needs covered, try selling goods to the TRAVELLING MERCHANTS, and upgrade your settlement. Good luck!

tip_pressToReadTip.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Click here to read the tip

tip_food_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Food is important, without it, the peasants can starve and regions rebel. There are few food sources in Manor Lords: {br}{br} Farming is slow, but provides a lot of food. It requires three buildings: FIELD, FARM, BARN. {br}{br} Hunters provide much less food, but also gather valuable hides. The only building required is the HUNTING CAMP {br}{br} Sheep can provide a bit more meat than hunting, and generate wool for sale. For this chain you need a SHEEP FARM, PASTURE & SLAUGHTERHOUSE. {br}{br}Choose your own path. You can upgrade every chain via the DEVELOPMENT TREE. You can also import food via the MERCHANT building.

focus_farming_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: This mission will shift the production focus of this region into agricultural development. The final products of this chain include Bread, Fruit, Beer & Linen clothes.
focus_farming_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Wykonanie tego zadania nakieruje region na specjalizację w rolnictwie.

focus_leather_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: This mission shifts the development region to leather production. The final products include Shoes, Belts and Saddles. It connects well with animal husbandry, as sheep can also be a great source of Pelts.

task_backToHitchingPost.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Going back to the Hitching Post

cropID_0_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Press to select the crop type for this field.

cropID_1_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: WHEAT can be processed into GRAIN, then into FLOUR and , finally to be consumed as FOOD, or processed further.

cropID_2_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: FLAX can be weaved into LINEN.

cropID_3_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Barley can be processed into MALT and then into ALE.

cropID_4_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Peat can be used as fuel for warming up the cottages in the winter, and cooking meals.

tutorial_welcome.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Welcome to the closed alpha of Manor Lords! {br}{br}The game has been going through a lot of reworks, and a lot of the industries are temporarily disabled. {br}{br}In the SETTINGS panel below you will find an option to play a test battle. {br}{br}Thanks for all the help and patience, {br}{br}Slavic Magic

tutorial_occasionalNeeds.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: This house requires a COMMODITY{br}If you're not producing this good in this region, it might be wise to build a MERCHANT'S HOUSE. The merchant can travel to a nearest TRADE POINT to aquire the nessecary goods in exchange for SILVER..

tutorial_taxation.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: REGIONAL WEALTH {br}This building has earned some SILVER. {br}{br}You can use it to:{br}-Import goods to fulfill COMMODITY REQUESTS{br}-Upgrade Housing to gain DEVELOPMENT POINTS{br}-Build a TAX COLLECTOR to pay the ROYAL TAXES.

tutorial_no_labour.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: <t>ASSIGNING WORKERS</> {br}You can now select this building to add or remove workers.
tutorial_no_labour.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: <t>PRZYDZIELANIE PRACOWNIKÓW</> {br}Kliknij na ten budynek, aby dodać lub odjąć pracowników.

tutorial_no_labour_field.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Build <h>FARM</> to plow the field, only after it's ploughed assign workers in order to sow seeds.
tutorial_no_labour_field.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Zbuduj farmę wołów, żeby zaorać pole. Potem przydziel pracowników, aby zasiać plony.

tutorial_construction_workers.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Unassigned peasants automatically work on construction. {br}If there is nothing to construct, they will help work in buildings with ENABLED IDLE LABOURERS switched on.
tutorial_construction_workers.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Nieprzydzieleni do zawodów chłopi budują samodzielnie. {br} Jeżeli nie ma czego budowaĆ DOKOŃCZ

tutorial_timber.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: <t>CAREFUL! YOU'RE ABOUT TO RUN OUT OF TIMBER AND BLOCK YOURSELF! </>{br}Make sure you have a Woodcutter Camp before placing more buildings.
tutorial_timber.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: CAREFUL! YOU'RE ABOUT TO RUN OUT OF TIMBER AND BLOCK YOURSELF! {br}Woodcutter Camp chops WOOD and Carpenter Camp converts them to TIMBER.

tutorial_healers.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: <t>IT'S GONNA BE TOUGH</>{br}Finding herbs during the winter is much harder than normal.

tutorial_stalls.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: <t>SELLING GOODS</>{br}One Merchant Stall can sell only one type of good. {br}The maximum inventory limit is 10 goods per employed worker.

tutorial_pops.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: WATCH OUT FOR SUPPLIES{br}Peasants are coming to your village! This is great, but watch out for your SUPPLIES. Hungry and cold peasants can rebel.

tutorial_fieldPlacing_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Some buildings have flexible borders. Place 4 points to designate an area.{br}The cursor will snap to the roads and buildings, to try and create an organic shape.{br}You can leave more space for future EXTENSION UPGRADES. {br}{br}First two points mark the front of the house by default.

tutorial_spoilingFood.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Build a <h>GRANARY</>. or employ more Granary workers.
tutorial_spoilingFood.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: SPOILING FOOD{br} Meat has to be storted in a LARDER, and all other types of food in a GRANARY. Otherwise - it will start to rot!

tutorial_foodBerries.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Low on food? {br}Try building a FORAGER HUT near the BERRY DEPOSIT.

tutorial_foodHunting.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Low on food?{br}Try building a HUNTING CAMP near the WILD ANIMALS habitat.

tutorial_selling.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: SELLING GOODS{br}You can sell goods, for example MATERIALS, on the Town Square to gain SILVER. {br}To create a Town Square, BUILD MARKET STALLS NEAR THE WELL.

tutorial_royalTaxes_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Since you've established a proper village, now the King will expect a payment every year. Check your ROYAL TAX amount in the top right corner of the screen.

tutorial_firewood_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Make sure to enable firewood production for the winter. After checking "Produce firewood", workers will convert Timber to Firewood so that people won't freeze. {br}{br}You can check your Supplies meter in the top bar to check if you have enough to survive.

tutorial_winning_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: To take other Lord's lands, you need Influence. The easiest way to gain Influence is to pay a type of tax called Tithe to the Church.{br}{br}Once you have enough influence you can press a Claim for a Region. To refute a Claim, the enemy Lord can challenge you to a battle.

tutorial_regionView.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: The Region View shows you which Regions are under whose control {br}You can claim other regions when you gain enough INFLUENCE . Claims can be refuted, or if a WAR is declared, blocked by the presence of an ENEMY ARMY. {br}{br}CONQUEST LOCKED IN THE DEMO

buildingID_1_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Increases walking speed by 10%. Peasants don't have to use roads, but they largely prefer it.
buildingID_1_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Zwiększa prędkość poruszania o 10%. Chłopi nie muszą używać dróg, lecz znacznie je preferują.

buildingID_2_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Must be built within a BAILEY.{br}{br}Provides living space for 5 peasants. {br}{br}(FEATURES LOCKED IN THE DEMO) Unlocks POLICIES in the region. Grants 150 INFLUENCE. {br}{br}Provides garrison space for the Retinue. First Manor built grants a free Retinue squad of 12.

buildingID_3_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Provides living space for 2 PEASANTS. {br}Must be close to a WELL. Can be upgraded to raise DEVELOPMENT.
buildingID_3_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Gwarantuje miejsce zamieszkania dla 2 CHŁOPÓW. {br}Musi być w okolicy STUDNI. Może zostać ulepszona aby zwiększyć POZIOM ROZWOJU/

buildingID_4_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Workers fell nearby trees to produce TIMBER for construction.

buildingID_5_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Can produce various CROPS, including WHEAT, FLAX & BARLEY. {br}{br}To employ peasants on the Fields, you need to build a FARM.

buildingID_6_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Sells surplus goods to passing TRAVELLING MERCHANTS. {br}{br}Optionally, workers travel to the nearest TRADEPOINT to buy or sell goods based on set stock targets. {br}{br}Trade is done using REGIONAL WEALTH.

buildingID_7_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Used to extract IRON ORE from IRON DEPOSITS and CLAY from CLAY DEPOSITS.
buildingID_7_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Umożliwia wydobycie RUDY ŻELAZA ze ZŁÓŻ ŻELAZA, oraz GLINY ze ZŁÓŻ GLINY.

buildingID_10_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Provides grazing space for SHEEP. Without enough space they won't breed. {br}{br}Breeding requires the SHEEPBEEDING development branch (LOCKED IN THE DEMO).
buildingID_10_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Udostępnia miejsce do pasania OWIEC. Bez odpowiedniej ilości miejsca na pastwisku, nie będą się rozmnażać.

buildingID_12_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: A TOWN CENTER MODULE. {br}{br}Enables selling goods to passing TRAVELLING MERCHANTS.
buildingID_12_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Moduł Centrum Miasta. Sprzedaje towar przejeżdżającym WOLONYM KUPCOM.

buildingID_13_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: An area for the Assigned Families to distribute their produce. Citizens setup stalls automatically.{br}{br}When supply meets demand, REQUIREMENTS of nearby houses are filled.

buildingID_14_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Workers hunt WILD ANIMALS in the region. Produces MEAT and PELTS.
buildingID_14_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Łowcy polują na DZIKIE ZWIERZĘTA w Regionie. Obóz produkuje MIĘSO i SKÓRY.

buildingID_19_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Enables <h>PLOUGHING</> up to 3 fields at the same time (one worker per field).
buildingID_19_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Umożliwia <h>ZAORANIE</> do trzech pól na raz (jeden chłop na jedno pole).

buildingID_20_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Converts GRAIN to FLOUR. {br}{br}Works most efficiently on empty land, unobstructed by buildings or trees.

buildingID_21_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Provides WATER ACCESS to the BURGAGE PLOTS. Enables FIREFIGHTING. {br}{br}Must be built over a WATER VEIN.

buildingID_25_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Uses IRON SLABS and FUEL to craft TOOLS.

buildingID_30_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Used to control OXEN. Oxen help in logistics by transporting construction TIMBER and can help with moving harvested crops to the GRANARY quicker.

buildingID_31_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Harvests WOOL from SHEEP {br}{br}Sheep must first be imported via the LIVESTOCK TRADER.

buildingID_33_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Converts WOOL into YARN, and FLAX into LINEN.

buildingID_34_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Grants access to FAITH for the Burgage Plots.

buildingID_36_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Foragers gather BERRIES from the nearby BERRY DEPOSIT.

buildingID_37_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Gives citizens of the Region access to ALE . Lowers PUBLIC ORDER.
buildingID_37_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Daje dostęp do ALE mieszkańcom regionu. Źle wpływa na PORZĄDEK PUBLICZNY.

buildingID_42_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Gathers STONE from nearby STONE DEPOSITS.
buildingID_42_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Zbiera KAMIEŃ z pobliskich ZŁÓŻ KAMIENIA.

buildingID_43_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Converts IRON ORE into IRON SLABS.

buildingID_50_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Create a closed walled perimeter to designate the area for your <h>MANORHOUSE</>. {br}{br}Requires a <h>GATEHOUSE</> for construction to start. {br}{br}Construction cost depends on the wall length.

buildingID_51_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Used to gather honey. {br}{br} Must be built on FLOWER FIELDS. Check Regional map to see resource availability.

buildingID_52_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Used to mine salt. {br}{br} Must be built on SALT DEPOSITS. Check Regional map to see resource availability.

buildingID_58_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Enables tax collection in the Region. Taxes transfer funds from <h>REGIONAL WEALTH</> into <h>PERSONAL TREASURY</>.

buildingID_69_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Used to employ Peasants on the FIELDS. {br}Farm workers plough the fields as soon as the Winter passes, then sow them with the chosen crop, harvest them in September. {br}{br}Then the crops are transported to the Farm, and Wheat is THRESHED into Grain.

buildingID_72_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Provides storage space for generic goods and logs to shield them from weather damage. {br}{br}Uses HANDCARTS to supply non-food related MARKET STALLS faster.

buildingID_73_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Provides living space for 1 FAMILY. {br}{br}When upgraded, grants a DEVELOPMENT POINT, and extra living space. {br}{br}If large enough, has slots for EXTENSIONS.

buildingID_74_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Allows buying and selling of LIVESTOCK to passing LIVESTOCK MERCHANTS for SILVER.

buildingID_76_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: After it's grown, periodically produces BRUSHWOOD. It can be collected by Woodcutter's Lodge workers.

buildingID_79_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Allows importing and exporting of LIVESTOCK for SILVER.

buildingID_80_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Stores up to 500 <h>FOOD</>. Helps supply the <h>FOOD STALLS</> faster

buildingID_87_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: After all homeless find accomodation, they're automatically removed.
buildingID_87_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Powstają gdy mieszkańcy nie mają domostw. Po znalezieniu miejsca zamieszkania zostają usunięte.

buildingID_89_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Workers chop down nearby trees to produce FIREWOOD.

buildingID_91_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Provides easy access to FOOD for BURGAGE PLOTS. {br}{br}Must be placed within the MARKETPLACE AREA.

buildingID_93_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Distributes CLOTH, LEATHER and YARN to the BURGAGE PLOTS.

buildingID_94_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Walled defensive area in which Manor buildings can be placed.
buildingID_94_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Ogrodzony teren, w którym można budować moduły twierdzy.

buildingID_98_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Under rework - just decorative in the current build.

building_destroyed_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Can be rebuilt, or taken apart for resources.
building_destroyed_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Może zostać odbudowany, lub rozebrany na surowce.

log_foodShortage_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: This region ran out of food stocks. If you don't do something, people are going to starve.
log_foodShortage_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Jedzenie w tym regionie niedługo się skończy. Jeśli czegoś nie zrobimy, ludzie zaczną głodować.

log_deerExtinction_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Due to overhunting the population of this animal may soon go extinct. Consider giving it some time to regrow.
log_deerExtinction_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Przez intensywne polowanie populacja tych zwierząt może ulec wyginięciu. Być może warto pozostawić zwierzynę samą sobie, aby miała czas się odrodzić.

taxType_0_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Basic tax <h>collected per family</> on the first day of the each month.
taxType_0_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Podstawowy podatek liczony od rodziny każdego pierwszego dnia miesiąca.

taxType_1_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: A tax gathered for <h>upkeep of mercenaries</>. Collected when paying for a mercenary unit.
taxType_1_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Podatek na utrzymanie najemników. Zbierany za każdym razem, gdy płacisz jednostce najemników.

taxType_2_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Gives away a percentage of goods to the CHURCH. It converts SILVER to INFLUENCE.
taxType_2_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Procent wszystkich dóbr z tego regionu przechodzi w posiadanie kościoła. W zamian otrzymujesz od kościoła taką samą ilość

taxType_3_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Collected whenever GRAIN is milled to FLOUR.

taxType_4_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Calculated from every transaction at the <h>MARKET STALLS</>.
taxType_4_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Odliczany od każdej transakcji na <h>STOISKACH HANDLOWYCH</>.

taxType_5_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Collected at the first day of the month only <h>in times of war</>.
taxType_5_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Pobierany na początku miesiąca <h>tylko w stanie wojny</>

tooltip_attractivenes_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Indicates how likely merchants are to travel through this Region. Depends on <h>amount of unique goods sold, with lowest prices</> compared to all the other Regions.
tooltip_attractivenes_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Wskazuje jak chętnie kupcy wybierają drogę przez ten region. Zależy od <h>ilości unikatowych dóbr o najniższych cenach</> na mapie.

tooltip_housing_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Peasants will come to your village if you build more COTTAGES. Immigration speed depends on LOYALTY
tooltip_housing_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Chłopi będą imigrować do wioski, gdy zbudujesz więcej CHAT. Szybkość imigracji zależy od LOJANLOŚCI.

tooltip_developmentLevel_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Press to open the <h>DEVELOPMENT TREE</>{br}{br}<h>Upgrade Cottages</> to raise the Development Level and unlock new <h>Development Branches</>.
tooltip_developmentLevel_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Kliknij by otworzyć <h>DRZEWKO ROZWOJU</>{br}{br}<h>Ulepszaj Chaty</> aby podnieść poziom rozwoju regionu i odblokować nowe <h>GAŁĘZIE ROZWOJU</>.

tooltip_developmentLevel_descr_nonClicka.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Spend silver on upgrading buildings in order to raise the Development Level and unlock new <h>Development Branches</>.
tooltip_developmentLevel_descr_nonClicka.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Wydawaj srebro na ulepszanie chat, aby podnieść poziom rozwoju regionu i odblokować nowe <h>GAŁĘZIE ROZWOJU</>.

tooltip_influence_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Influence can be traded via the diplomacy system. Can be gained by giving taxes to the Church, rising population, building new Manors and improving the development.

tooltip_favour_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Every year the most influential Lord or Lady is being awarded with the King's Favour. {br}{br}Can be spend to claim new territories (more options to come later).

tooltip_challenge_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: The last man standing wins the Claim. If time runs out, the Claim is refuted.

tooltip_public_order_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Low public order causes crime and banditry. Influenced by alcohol consumption, prostitution, church presence, approval rate, unemployment and town watch patrols.

policySlot_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Press to see policies available in this region.

policySlot_locked_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Build a <h>MANOR</> to enable enacting policies in this region.

policyID_1_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Peasants eat half as often, in effect consuming less FOOD and RAW WOOD. {br}{br} Loyalty falls by 0.5% each day.
policyID_1_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Chłopi dwa razy rzadziej jedzą posiłki, zużywając przez to mniej JEDZENIA, oraz SUROWEGO DREWNA. {br}{br} LOJALNOŚĆ SPADA o 0.5% każdego dnia.

policyID_2_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: WILD ANIMALS breed twice as fast.{br}{br} CROPS WILL GET DAMAGED.
policyID_2_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: DZIKIE ZWIERZĘTA rozmnażają się dwa razy szybciej. {br}{br} PLONY BĘDA DEWASTOWANE.

tag_legprotection_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: +1 defense when mounted, +1 defense when in Spearwall, -1 stamina, -5% speed

tag_blunt_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: +2 attack against unist with heavy armour.

tag_spearwall_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: <h>SPECIAL ABILITY</> {br}Grants +10 defense when attacked from the front and self inflicts enemy's charge bonus. Immobile while in this stance.

tag_mounted_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: +1 attack, +1 defense, +10 charge. <h>Adds primary weapon - Lance. </>

recruitmentCost_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Paid once upfront, then once every month (at the same day of the month as hired)
recruitmentCost_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Płacony jednokrotnie od ręki, a później każdego miesiąca (w tym samym dniu miesiąca, w którym zostali zrekrutowani).

cant_afford.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Not enough silver in the region

skill2_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Slows down the unit significantly {br} Increases melee advantage due to higher UNITY {br} Grants SHIELDWALL to shielded units: If a soldier has friends on his side, it adds their block to his.{br} Grants IMPALING to immobile spear units: Reflects the enemies charge attack.

skill8_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Stops the unit in place and cancels its current target.
skill8_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Zatrzymuje jednostkę w miejscu i usuwa bieżący cel ataku.

skill9_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Makes unit moves faster, causing more <h>FATIGUE</>.

friendly_fire_mode_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Governs whether the soldiers should release arrows even if there's a possibility to hit a friend.
friendly_fire_mode_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Rozkazuje strzelać nawet jeżeli istnieje ryzyko trafienia swoich.

spoiled_food_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: MEAT has to be stored in a Larder, all other FOOD in a Granary. Otherwise it can SPOIL!

problemID_0_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: People require more FOOD. Starved peasants may die.

problemID_3_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Select the building if you wish to assign Workers.

problemID_8_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Sick villagers need to rest at home to recover. Consuming <h>HERBS</> speeds up the process.

problemID_9_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Build a Church, and free up one family to handle the burial

problemID_14_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: These workers have nothing to do. Perhaps it's best to assign them elsewhere?

problemID_17_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Peasant wanting to craft or sell a resource can't find it in this Region

problemID_18_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Build Cottages to provide them with shelter, or their APPROVAL will fall and they might freeze in the WINTER.

problemID_19_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: FOOD has to be moved to a GRANARY, otherwise it has a chance to spoil.
problemID_19_descr.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: MEAT has to be stored in a LARDER, and other types of FOOD in a GRANARY.

problemID_20_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: All Burgage Plot requirements for upgrading have been met.

problemID_21_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Peasants may occasionally require COMMODITIES. You need to import them via a MERCHANT, or LOYALTY will fall.

problemID_22_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Make sure you have enough FOOD and FUEL in storage.

problemID_27_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: You can spent SILVER accumulated in this household to gain a passive resource income.

problemID_28_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: No more resources to gather in the work area.

problemID_29_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: This building has no proper road connection. Handcarts and Merchants might not find a way to it. Make sure the ROAD CONNECTION POINTS are properly connected.

problemID_30.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Not connected to a trade route

problemID_30_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Merchants won't be able to find this Market Square. Make sure it's ROAD CONNECTION POINT is properly connected to a Trade Road.

problemID_32_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Build more Granaries or employ more Granary workers.

problemID_38_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: People are unhappy and might leave the town.

problemID_39_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: This residential plot has unfilled needs that cause a loss of <h>APPROVAL</>.

field_too_big.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Not enough workforce yet for this field size!
field_too_big.polish_4_FAC0A9B840141714A0A994BFF2FFBC7: Może nie starczyć rąk do pracy, aby obrobić to pole!

rotting_crops_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: If crops aren't transported into the farm or granary for a long time, they tend to rot.

target_inventory_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Sell livestock if above threshold, try to buy if below threshold.

trait_criminals_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Lower influence by 100 with every payment.

not_enough_silver.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: Not enough silver in the Treasury

mode_peaceful_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: The AI never attacks. Good for learning the mechanics.

mode_competitive_descr.english_2_067882A64F9EB32AAD3BA7BCE1822B: AI will try its best to win the game.
